2026-06-19  Qaaxaap  <1515784026@qq.com>

	* configure.ac: Add AC_PROG_RANLIB for static library support.
	* src/Makefile.am: Add noinst_LIBRARIES = liblfspkg.a target.
	Split library sources (db, package, util, elf) from CLI binary
	sources (main, cli).  lfspkg binary links against liblfspkg.a.
	* include/lfspkg/db.hpp (PackageMeta): Add built_deps field
	(std::map<std::string, std::string>) to record each dependency's
	version at build time.
	* src/db.cpp (write_meta_atomic): Serialize built_deps as
	"built_deps=dep1:ver1,dep2:ver2,...".
	(read_meta): Deserialize built_deps from meta file.
	* include/lfspkg/package.hpp: Declare find_stale_packages().
	* src/package.cpp (apply_install_or_upgrade): Resolve each dep's
	current version from the database and store in built_deps before
	writing PackageMeta.
	(find_stale_packages): New function.  For each installed package,
	compare built_deps versions against currently-installed dependency
	versions.  Returns names of packages with version mismatches.
	* ChangeLog: This file.

